<ul>
<li>Assigned <a style="text-decoration:none;" href="https://engineering.nyu.edu/academics/digital-learning-services/online-student-support">academic advisor</a> or advising team to help create a path toward degree completion</li>
<li>Designated learning management system <a style="text-decoration:none;" href="https://www.nyu.edu/life/information-technology/teaching-and-learning-services/instructional-tools/nyu-lms-brightspace.html">NYU Brightspace</a>, for course navigation</li>
<li>Assistance with academic transitioning into online and graduate studies</li>
<li>Online access to <a style="text-decoration:none;" href="https://library.nyu.edu/">NYU Libraries</a> including daily access to a virtual librarian</li>
<li>Supplemental learning resources to refresh and reinforce fundamental concepts</li>
</ul>
