            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-landing-accordion-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>Build meaningful connections through collaboration and networking between students, learners, alumni, faculty, and industry to foster a robust community of interdisciplinary professionals at NYU.</p>
