            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-styled-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h2>Digital Learning Alumni</h2>
<p>Lifelong learning is core to NYU Tandon’s mission and Digital Learning alumni receive exclusive benefits to support continuous learning and further career advancement.</p>
<ul>
<li>Receive a 20% Alumni scholarship toward <a href="https://engineering.nyu.edu/academics/programs/professional-education">Executive &amp; Professional Education</a> programs</li>
<li>Share your technical knowledge and professional experience by engaging with the Digital Learning community</li>
<li>Retain access to <a href="https://engineering.nyu.edu/life-tandon/tandon-career-hub/resources-alumni">career development</a> as you continue to progress in your career</li>
<li>Join the broader <a href="https://www.nyu.edu/alumni.html">NYU Alumni</a> &amp; <a href="https://engineering.nyu.edu/engage/alumni">NYU Tandon Alumni Association</a> for even more benefits</li>
</ul>
